@page "/"

<PageTitle>PromptAgent - Prompt 優化測試系統</PageTitle>

<div class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-badge">
            <span class="badge-icon">⚡</span>
            <span>AI Powered</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">
            <span class="gradient-text">Prompt</span>Agent
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
            智慧化的 Prompt 優化測試系統<br />
            多輪平行測試 × AI 評估分析 × 一鍵優化
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="prompt-test" class="btn-primary">
                <span class="btn-icon">🧪</span>
                開始測試
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
            <h3>多輪平行執行</h3>
            <p>使用 Task.WhenAll 同時執行多個 Agent，快速測試 Prompt 穩定性</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
            <h3>AI 智慧評估</h3>
            <p>由更強的 AI 模型 (GPT-5) 分析結果，給出專業評估報告</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">✨</div>
            <h3>一鍵優化建議</h3>
            <p>自動生成優化後的 Prompt，一鍵套用立即改善效果</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📋</div>
            <h3>預設測試範例</h3>
            <p>內建數學運算、邏輯推理、翻譯等多種測試範例</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
